{"tid":1658931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉事務處即時起至周五下午暫停供公眾查閱選民登記冊","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:05:23.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"530e2da682647557957db0e00bce5b230adb553d","tid":1658931,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處宣布，即時起至本星期五下午4時30分，2019年正式選民/投票人登記冊暫停供公眾查閱及向任何人提供選民資料。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察隊員佐級協會入稟申請司法覆核，要求頒下緊急臨時禁制令，禁止選舉登記主任提供2019年正式選民/投票人登記冊予公眾查閱及其他。<br />\n<br />\n原訴法庭聆訊後，駁回員佐級協會的申請，但頒下短期的臨時禁制令，選舉事務處由即時起至本星期五下午4時30分期間，這些資料不得供公眾查閱及向任何人提供選民資料，以給予時間員佐級協會一方考慮會否上訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486628-20191017.htm?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486628-20191017.htm%3F&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=1b9b2c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486628-20191017.htm%3F&h=751c8fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486628-20191017.htm?</a>"},{"pid":"05b865709b28281bec7224e4d370f7f177d9d080","tid":1658931,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"55756d02f067f979d1f3637ccbb6964227289abb","tid":1658931,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"軍政府連選舉都想控制埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d9a4d2250ff670497c2962a10b3187dcaf9516","tid":1658931,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score